Distribution. This species occurs in a wide, partially scattered range from south-western France , southern and northern Italy , central and eastern Europe, through the Balkans, the Ukraine , the Baltic states, southern Russia and Turkey to the Middle East, the Caucasus region, the Caspian Sea coast and northern Iran ( Laštůvka & Laštůvka 1995 , 2001 ,
Špatenka et al. 1999
).

Note. Most of the standard literature (e.g.
Špatenka et al. 1999
) cites 1842 as publication year for this taxon. However, we follow the conclusions of Olivier (2000) and consider 1843 the year of publication.
